Question: Explain how to reach your home without using any street names
Answer:
From the highway going north, once you pass the CVS, take a right.  Continue on that road until you reach a four way intersection by the corner store.  Proceed straight through.  Continue until you get to a fork then go right.  Take the second left.  At the fork, go left, then take a right at the dirt road with multiple mailboxes and go to the end.